title: Andrei Otyutsky
text:
Andrei Ivanovich Otyutsky (; born 27 April 1982) is a former <a href="Russia">Russia</a>n professional <a href="Association%20football">football</a>er.
Club career.
He made his debut in the <a href="Russian%20Premier%20League">Russian Premier League</a> in 2001 for <a href="FC%20Dynamo%20Moscow">FC Dynamo Moscow</a>.
